@Solidsoldier- that's possibly the most awkward combo ever. Try Vesper Ghoul with [Freed from the real](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Freed from the real), double [Bazaar Trader](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bazaar Trader) or [Donate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Donate)s and [Mindslaver](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mindslaver) instead.  
Results may vary.  
Also I'd like to note that this would be such a very awesome card if it weren't for the casting cost. 1B would've made a great card, even BB would be sweet. I mean look at the art, look at the flavour text, look at the creature type. It's a zombie frickin druid!

